9 AS INTRODUCED
10 An Act relating to motor vehicles; amending Section
1, Chapter 214, O.S.L. 2022 (47 O.S. Supp. 2024,
11 Section 1-133.1a), which relates to the definition of
military surplus vehicles; modifying definition of
12 military surplus vehicles; requiring military surplus
vehicles operated on the streets and highways be
13 registered by certain date; exempting certain
vehicles from fines; and providing an effective date.
14
15
16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 1, Chapter 214, O.S.L.
18 2022 (47 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 1-133.1a), is amended to read as
19 follows:
20 Section 1-133.1a Military surplus vehicle.
21 A. A "military surplus vehicle" is any motor vehicle having:
22 1. Three axles or fewer that meet the legal size and weight
23 limits set forth in Section 14-103 of Title 47 of the Oklahoma
24 Statutes this title;
